The Formation of Islamic Art
Yale University Press | 1978 | ISBN: 0300021879 | English | 340 pages | PDF | 30 MB

A book of absorbing interest and immense erudition. . . . All Islamic archaeologists and scholars will thank Professor Grabar for a profound and original study of an immense and complex field, which may provoke controversy but must impress by its mastery and charm by its modesty
